<D>__{healthy kid, too. didn't waste any time getting out.}
<A>__{vanessa reaches out for the baby and gingerly accepts him in her eyes. she spends a few moments just looking at him. she feels someone watching her, then looks up to see a bren leaning against the doorway. vanessa blinks away her tears self consciously.}
